  "## How CSPR.fans Sybil mechanics actually work, on-chain",
  "",
  "Casper's marketing said the vote was Sybil-resistant. CSPR.fans is the Telegram mini-app where, per the official rules, \"You'll be able to send up to 1,000 FAN points per day to your favorite project(s).\" Users earn those points by following Casper on X, watching YouTube videos, downloading the Casper Wallet, and inviting friends — referral-compounded. The mechanism we measured on-chain works like this:",
