  "3. The signed message is submitted on-chain as a deploy to the FANR2 voting contract.",
  "4. The contract verifies the signature against the Association's signing key and **mints new FANR2 tokens directly to the recipient project**. There is no balance debit on the voter side. There is no on-chain supply cap.",
